---
const posts = [
  {
    title: "本周美股科技股观察：AI算力主线仍然强势",
    date: "2026-05-24",
    category: "市场周报",
    desc: "从AI算力、半导体、云计算、数据中心、宏观利率和估值风险等角度，复盘本周美股科技股表现，并总结后续重点观察方向。",
    link: "/articles/us-tech-weekly-2026-05-24"
  },
       {
     title: "2026-05-14 调仓收益记录",
     date: "2026-05-14",
     category: "调仓收益记录",
     desc: "本次调仓收益记录",
     link: "/articles/stock_hold_2026-05-14"
   },
     {
     title: "2026-04-16 调仓收益记录",
     date: "2026-04-16",
     category: "调仓收益记录",
     desc: "本次调仓收益记录",
     link: "/articles/stock_hold_2026-04-16"
   },

];
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>398的美股策略</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        background: #f5f7fb;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      header {
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(
            rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.65),
            rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75)
          ),
          url("/images/hero-bg.jpg");

        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;

        color: white;
        padding: 56px 10% 72px;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 72px;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      nav a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-left: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
        opacity: 0.92;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .hero {
        max-width: 820px;
      }

      .site-title {
        font-size: 46px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        font-weight: 900;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 19px;
        line-height: 1.9;
        opacity: 0.95;
      }

      .tags {
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 56px auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
      }

      .intro {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 42px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .intro h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .intro p {
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(290px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      }

      .category {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #1d4ed8;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .card h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        margin: 8px 0 10px;
      }

      .card p {
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .date {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }

      .read-more {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 16px;
        color: #1d4ed8;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .read-more:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 54px;
        background: #eef2ff;
        border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 22px 26px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #374151;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        padding: 42px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        header {
          padding: 36px 24px 56px;
        }

        nav {
          display: block;
          margin-bottom: 52px;
        }

        nav div:last-child {
          margin-top: 18px;
        }

        nav a {
          margin-left: 0;
          margin-right: 18px;
        }

        .site-title {
          font-size: 36px;
        }
      }
            .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 54px;
        background: #eef2ff;
        border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 22px 26px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #374151;
      }

      /* 订阅框样式放这里 */
      .subscribe-box {
        margin-top: 54px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      }

      .subscribe-box h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .subscribe-box p {
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .subscribe-box form {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .subscribe-box input {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .subscribe-box button {
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #2563eb;
        color: white;
        font-weight: 800;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .subscribe-box button:hover {
        background: #1d4ed8;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        padding: 42px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <div class="logo">398 的美股策略</div>
        <div>
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <a href="/about">关于我</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="site-title">398的美股策略</div>
        <div class="subtitle">
          用数据识别趋势，用规则减少情绪<br />
        </div>

        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">美股基本面分析</span>
          <span class="tag">策略复盘</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <h1>简介</h1>
        <p>
    这是一个记录美股科技股研究、纳斯达克市场观察和量化策略复盘的网站。
        </p>
      </section>

      <h1 class="section-title">最新文章</h1>

      <section class="grid">
        {posts.map((post) => (
          <article class="card">
            <div class="category">{post.category}</div>
            <h2>{post.title}</h2>
            <div class="date">{post.date}</div>
            <p>{post.desc}</p>
            <a class="read-more" href={post.link}>阅读全文 →</a>
          </article>
        ))}
      </section>
      
      <section class="subscribe-box">
        <h2>订阅我的美股投策更新</h2>
        <p>输入邮箱后，当发布新的市场观察或调仓记录时，你会收到邮件提醒。</p>

        <form
          action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/yufang"
          method="post"
          class="embeddable-buttondown-form"
        >
          <label for="bd-email">Enter your email</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" id="bd-email" />
          <input type="submit" value="Subscribe" />
          <p>
            <a href="https://buttondown.com/refer/yufang" target="_blank">
              Powered by Buttondown.
            </a>
          </p>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="disclaimer">
        <strong>风险提示：</strong>
        本网站所有内容仅为个人投研记录，不构成任何证券投资建议，
        不作为买入、卖出或持有任何证券的依据。投资有风险，入市需谨慎。
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © 2026 398的美股策略 ｜ 个人投研记录，不构成投资建议
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
